00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:32.740
to the second derivative.

00:14:32.740 --> 00:14:36.280
And it's non-stochastic, so
I'll explain why it's this.

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:38.300
But if you do it-- if you
look at this equation,

00:14:38.300 --> 00:14:41.190
