00:52:39.590 --> 00:52:43.170
And there is like a fundamental
derivative in the interest rate

00:52:43.170 --> 00:52:45.000
world is a LIBOR swap.

00:52:45.000 --> 00:52:47.250
So the standard USD LIBOR
swap is something like this,

00:52:47.250 --> 00:52:47.750
basically.

00:52:47.750 --> 00:52:51.520
It's paying-- once
