00:56:38.720 --> 00:56:39.220
right?

00:56:39.220 --> 00:56:41.770
So if I enter a swap--
so I know that the I will

00:56:41.770 --> 00:56:44.380
be paying fixed--
but I'll receive

00:56:44.380 --> 00:56:48.970
floating, which is
random, because we

