00:57:43.885 --> 00:57:49.285
we typically-- what is called
PV or present value of all

00:57:49.285 --> 00:57:50.910
our future payments, right?

00:57:50.910 --> 00:57:53.840
So we have some future
liability, which

00:57:53.840 --> 00:57:55.252
is something very complicated.

00:57:55.252 --> 00:57:57.210
I say, I'll pay you
something very complicated,

00:57:57.210 --> 00:57:59.260
pay off in 10 years from now.

00:57:59.260 --> 00:58:02.120
But we are trying to understand
how much it's worth today.

00:58:02.120 --> 00:58:05.620
Because idea for this business
is clients come to the bank.

00:58:05.620 --> 00:58:07.530
And they say, I want
