00:58:13.950 --> 00:58:15.650
because you need to
still make living.

00:58:15.650 --> 00:58:18.780
But in [INAUDIBLE] basically
is like you've spent

00:58:18.780 --> 00:58:20.530
most of your money on hedging.

00:58:23.840 --> 00:58:25.975
But you to try to come
up with a number today.

00:58:28.710 --> 00:58:31.730
Here's, again, a
very simple example.

00:58:31.730 --> 00:58:38.150
So if you know, once again,
how much your dollar is

00:58:38.150 --> 00:58:41.640
in the future, then
you can present

00:58:41.640 --> 00:58:43.720
value, PV, every payment.

00:58:43.720 --> 00:58:47.900
So let's say in 10 years
