00:58:52.450 --> 00:58:55.090
Because, again, the argument
is very simple, right?

00:58:55.090 --> 00:58:59.200
You take $500 today and
invest for 10 years,

00:58:59.200 --> 00:59:01.060
and you get $1,000
in the future.

00:59:01.060 --> 00:59:03.180
This is the
