the derivatives have become

01:00:27.690 --> 01:00:29.217
what's called collateralized.

01:00:29.217 --> 01:00:31.050
So you need to post
some money all the time.

01:00:31.050 --> 01:00:32.966
So there's another concept
of OIS discounting,

01:00:32.966 --> 01:00:35.292
