it mathematically and price

01:01:32.340 --> 01:01:33.820
all kinds of derivatives.

01:01:33.820 --> 01:01:37.800
So there is like a very
interesting difference

01:01:37.800 --> 01:01:45.720
between stock options
and interest rate options

01:01:45.720 --> 01:01:49.000
because for the stock options,
we know the price today.

01:01:49.000 --> 01:01:50.760
If it's a liquid
stock, it's just known.

01:01:50.760 --> 01:01:52.440
We know what it's
