01:02:02.330 --> 01:02:03.940
The next step, we
need to specify

01:02:03.940 --> 01:02:06.720
the volatility of different
forward rates in the future

01:02:06.720 --> 01:02:12.570
and we need to come up
with some kind of dynamics

01:02:12.570 --> 01:02:15.790
which describes the future
dynamics of forward rates.

01:02:15.790 --> 01:02:17.590
And then once we
have this, we can

01:02:17.590 --> 01:02:21.500
use the Monte Carlo framework to
price all kinds of derivatives.

01:02:21.500 --> 01:02:25.435
So before I start talking
